20
00:02:00,750 --> 00:02:02,140
SPEAKER_08: Chalk it up.

21
00:02:12,889 --> 00:02:14,150
SPEAKER_08: How much?

72
00:07:56,370 --> 00:07:59,459
SPEAKER_08: All right, do it yourself. But please don't cry.

73
00:08:01,509 --> 00:08:02,730
SPEAKER_08: Fugui...

90
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:33,250
SPEAKER_08: Well?

227
00:24:07,170 --> 00:24:08,970
SPEAKER_08: Just call me Fugui.

239
00:24:45,980 --> 00:24:48,880
SPEAKER_08: I'd like to borrow money to set up a shop.

240
00:24:53,549 --> 00:24:56,710
SPEAKER_08: I'm not one to lend money.

241
00:24:58,190 --> 00:25:03,150
SPEAKER_08: I'll lend you something else. More practical.

242
00:25:10,829 --> 00:25:13,930
SPEAKER_08: I never had to beg
when I ran the puppet troupe.

348
00:44:41,269 --> 00:44:44,000
SPEAKER_08: Mother died without knowing where I was.

349
00:44:46,679 --> 00:44:48,010
SPEAKER_08: The day...

350
00:44:48,880 --> 00:44:52,510
SPEAKER_08: we sang for the Liberation Army.

351
00:44:55,320 --> 00:44:58,179
SPEAKER_08: Suppose I was singing for her, too.

355
00:45:13,739 --> 00:45:15,260
SPEAKER_08: Written?

356
00:45:15,340 --> 00:45:19,000
SPEAKER_08: I never thought I'd make it back alive.

544
01:01:51,670 --> 01:01:53,690
SPEAKER_08: Daddy will make it better.

545
01:01:57,940 --> 01:01:59,909
SPEAKER_08: Youqing, after dinner...

546
01:02:00,940 --> 01:02:02,599
SPEAKER_08: come see the show.

547
01:02:02,679 --> 01:02:05,699
SPEAKER_08: Youqing's not going to any stupid show.

548
01:02:11,920 --> 01:02:16,909
SPEAKER_08: He uses the secret mirror

549
01:02:20,389 --> 01:02:25,420
SPEAKER_08: and blinds all who look within

550
01:02:40,210 --> 01:02:45,210
SPEAKER_08: I yell there's no time to waste

551
01:03:11,110 --> 01:03:16,139
SPEAKER_08: Far away, we flee with haste

610
01:10:47,239 --> 01:10:50,569
SPEAKER_08: Must not be politically backward.
