611
01:10:51,840 --> 01:10:54,670
SPEAKER_08: Are 15 dumplings enough?

612
01:10:57,710 --> 01:11:00,239
SPEAKER_08: Have 20. You should eat more.

613
01:11:12,529 --> 01:11:15,619
SPEAKER_08: Youqing, wake up. We're nearly there.

741
01:25:00,520 --> 01:25:02,149
SPEAKER_08: Delivering water is fine.

742
01:25:02,220 --> 01:25:06,289
SPEAKER_08: Jiazhen's health is poor.
If we're together, I can look after her.

881
01:38:17,319 --> 01:38:19,180
SPEAKER_08: Sit with us for a bit.

882
01:38:19,750 --> 01:38:21,479
SPEAKER_08: Don't be like that.

928
01:42:21,300 --> 01:42:23,289
SPEAKER_08: Don't bring up the past.

929
01:42:23,930 --> 01:42:25,800
SPEAKER_08: I was a real no-hoper.

932
01:42:32,670 --> 01:42:34,229
SPEAKER_08: Erxi, drink up.

976
01:46:09,289 --> 01:46:11,189
SPEAKER_08: You mustn't lose hope.

1052
01:51:29,640 --> 01:51:31,470
SPEAKER_08: Who examined Fengxia?

1112
01:56:30,310 --> 01:56:33,680
SPEAKER_08: Erxi's is a work-related injury.
It's not hereditary.

1220
02:05:07,390 --> 02:05:09,020
SPEAKER_08: I'll make lunch.

1264
